text: So a wee update on my exciting day. I didn't break my arm, but dislocated my elbow pretty convincingly. Massive thanks to London Ambulance service, Kingston Hospital, the staff at White Spider climbing wall and @allanrmacneil and Thom for sticking with me through the whole thing! https://t.co/3I7clFRhue
Going out in London last night made me realise how shit Kingston and bmouth clubs are
